## End of Report

This report provides a comprehensive analysis of the state of education in rural Uttar Pradesh. It highlights the challenges and opportunities in the education sector and provides recommendations for policymakers and practitioners.

We hope that this report will contribute to the ongoing dialogue on education in India and help to improve the quality of education for all children.

